<div class="form-group">
  <label class="control-label col-md-3">State</label>
  <div class="col-md-9 input-fragment">
    <div class="label-vertical">The state determines whether a DOI is registered in the global Handle System and if its metadata is publicly available. Once in Registered or Findable state, a DOI cannot be deleted. <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://support.datacite.org/docs/doi-states">Learn more&nbsp;â€¦</a></div>
    <div><RadioButton @value="draft" @groupValue={{this.state}} @radioClass="radio" @changed={{action "selectStateAction"}} @disabled={{this.draft}} />Draft <span class="help-block">the DOI is not yet registered in the global Handle System, does not need to have valid metadata or a URL, and can be deleted</span></div>
    <div><RadioButton @value="registered" @groupValue={{this.state}} @radioClass="radio" @changed={{action "selectStateAction"}} @disabled={{this.registered}} />Registered <span class="help-block">the DOI is registered in the global Handle System, but its metadata is not publicly available</span></div>
    <div><RadioButton @value="findable" @groupValue={{this.state}} @radioClass="radio" @changed={{action "selectStateAction"}} @disabled={{this.findable}} />Findable <span class="help-block">the DOI is registered in the global Handle System and its metadata is publicly available</span></div>
  </div>
</div>
